# quoted-key-single-all-escapes

## Input

```mical
'k\\1' v1
'k\"2' v2
'k\'3' v3
'k\n4' v4
'k\r5' v5
'k\t6' v6

```

## JSON

```json
{
  "k\\1": "v1",
  "k\"2": "v2",
  "k'3": "v3",
  "k\n4": "v4",
  "k\r5": "v5",
  "k\t6": "v6"
}
```

